<h2 id="create-points-on-a-map">Create Points on a Map</h2>

<p>This tutorial shows how you can create a feature class and populate it with point features.  You can find the tutorial instructions <a href="https://pro.arcgis.com/en/pro-app/latest/get-started/create-points-on-a-map.htm">here</a> or watch the video below.</p>

